\SE[1]By the way, I've been meaning to ask. Luna... Oh, um,
is Luna Roa a famous person?

Famous person... you mean Luna Roa, right? She is one of the
few special scholarship students in the history of the magic
academy, who has managed to maintain the top position for
five years straight, even while yawning...

She even published a book that challenged existing
principles, and on top of that, she obtained seven doctoral
degrees... But it feels like I haven't heard this directly
from her?
\SE[10]I don't really know much about Luna's school...

It seems like there were various things going on over
there... But it's not really appropriate for an outsider
like me to talk so freely.

You're Luna Roa's lover, right? I'm sure she'll tell you
about it eventually.

\SE[11]That's right... um, how did they find out about our
relationship too?

Ahaha...! Just by looking at your eyes, I can tell that
much. Ah... being young is nice, isn't it...

Welcome back. So, how was it? Does it seem like it will work
out?
I could see the logic behind it. I think it's possible...

...Alright! Go ahead and rest in bed. I won't be sleeping
tonight.

If there's anything I can help with, please let me know.
Whether it's making tea or being a guinea pig, I'll do
anything!

Hehe... Then, will you stay by my side? If you're there with
a smile, I feel like I can do anything.
Supporting each other in love... Ahh... that's nice.
